description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a Physiotherapy Technical Instructor/ Assistant to join the Trauma &amp; Orthopaedic inpatient team at Wrexham Maelor Hospital.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The successful candidate will support the physiotherapists and the multi disciplinary team to provide physiotherapy intervention and facilitate hospital discharges.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Training and on going development will be available from a supportive, established team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date: 9th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dave Massey&lt;br /&gt;E-mail: dave.massey@wales.nhs.uk&lt;br /&gt;Tel: 01978 727789&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cindy Wakenshaw&lt;br /&gt;E-mail: cindy.wakenshaw@wales.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
